		</TD>
		<TD>
		$ <INPUT TYPE="TEXT" NAME="net12" SIZE="8" readonly>
		</TD>
	</TR>
	<TR BGCOLOR="#EEEEDD">
		<TD>
		Advantage of Waiting:
		</TD>
		<TD>
		&nbsp;
